.朋友 重質不重量不重時間長短。<br />\n<br />\n希望你會遇見到合適你嘅朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:48:46.000Z","msg":"係 所以我quit咗了<br />\n一個朋友都無了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝你"},{"pid":"c0cfd51e524d52f5946851ed89649b2fd72baf5b","tid":1856380,"uid":215861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40f192bb2f0c950e87a58818a419d0ec4b5f2d4f","tid":1856380,"uid":110555,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:15:14.000Z","msg":"付出真心交朋友，係無錯。唔係你唔配有朋友，係佢地唔配擁有你呢個朋友！<br />\n<br />\n但你錯在識唔到懂得珍惜你、欣賞你好嘅朋友。關係喺雙向架，唔喺你對人地有幾好就得，都要對方重視你先得。簡單啲講，就好似暗戀同相戀嘅分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者你同人做朋友前，除咗睇啱唔啱傾同埋價值觀外，都要睇下個個人會唔會珍惜你、重視你呢。<br />\n<br />\n相信我，真正嘅朋友係會包容你嘅缺點，提醒你扶持你，同你一齊成長，而最重要係唔會輕易離開你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無咗呢班酒肉朋友唔可惜，最可惜可能係你會因為佢地而放棄去對朋友好/害怕付出真心識朋友。希望你唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"我都期望會有個可以同我一齊成長嘅好朋友⋯"},{"pid":"5df27226c854ca1d8061941e2f5b92ef26ca9c16","tid":1856380,"uid":215861,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e64b23d80020a2848daea493f96470b0f6c47d93","tid":1856380,"uid":71712,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓G好樣衰?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"同池美麗差唔多啦"},{"pid":"f52bd320311aa56b357e5576c9b0203465dce40a","tid":1856380,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:50:28.000Z","msg":"會唔會係你問題"},{"pid":"a6ac82509a8f2ac98004aafef10d2ab60fab4d18","tid":1856380,"uid":215861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e651790787379b77851c871b83a92e45c6342e8e","tid":1856380,"uid":317335,"like":8,"di